  "invariants": [
    "cursor is optional and accepts a number or numeric string; omission means 0, then reuse next_cursor",
    "the trail is daemon-global and may expose operation subjects/paths from other clients of the same daemon",
    "rows are ordered by increasing audit_id and bounded by the daemon audit-read cap",
    "action_filter and decision_filter are optional exact-match filters",
    "an empty rows array is a valid success response only when the daemon is reachable",
    "daemon unavailable is a typed daemon_unavailable error, not empty success"
  ]
